  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> sleep up to two adults and are around 20m². They've been finished in a traditional style and facilities include air conditioning, minibar, TV, safe and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are 26m² and are elegantly decorated. They have garden views from the balcony and sleep up to two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are about 31 - 35<span>m²</span> and available with garden views from the large windows. Or, you can upgrade to a sea view for a supplement. They can sleep up to three people.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are about <span>40m</span>² and have a separate living room and lovely terrace with garden views. The rooms may be on split levels with the living area on the lower floor and the bedroom on the mezzanine. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Sea View Suites</strong> with sweeping sea views sleep up to three people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Single Rooms</strong> are a great choice for solo travellers. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
